In Pennsylvania, Beaver, Washington, Allegheny, Armstrong, Higher Elevations of Indiana, Indiana, and Westmoreland Counties. In West Virginia, Hancock and Brooke Counties.
entry.cap:areaDesc: Brooke; Hancock

entry.title: Winter Storm Watch issued October 23 at 2:37AM MDT until October 26 at 6:00PM MDT by NWS
entry.summary: ...WINTER STORM WATCH IN EFFECT FROM WEDNESDAY MORNING THROUGH THURSDAY AFTERNOON... * WHAT...Heavy snow possible. Total snow accumulations of 10 to 20 inches possible. Winds could gust as high as 45 mph. * WHERE...Yellowstone National Park, Absaroka Mountains and Teton and Gros Ventre Mountains.
entry.cap:areaDesc: Absaroka Mountains; Teton and Gros Ventre Mountains; Yellowstone National Park
